* &quot;Dujang Prang&quot; (1995) 
* &quot;2007&quot; (1999) 
* &quot;Station&quot; (2007) 
* &quot;It&quot; (2017) recordings from 2010-2016
* &quot;Mutator&quot; (2021) recordings from 1995-1996
* &quot;Insurrection&quot; (2024) recordings from 1997-1998.

